  Locus:
    Page: 115
    Verse: 8
Tags:
  - Ego
---
Anyone who serves God will discover sooner or later that the great hinder-
ance to his work is not others but himself. He will discover that his
outward man and his inward man are not in harmony, for both are tending
toward opposite directions.
